:

1. *Karijeru* je veoma teško uspešno završiti. (It is very difficult to successfully complete a career.)
2. Pomoću dobre *karijere* možete postići svoje ciljeve. (With a good career you can achieve your goals.)
3. Ona je uspela da napreduje u svojoj *karijeri*. (She succeeded in progressing in her career.)
4. Možda će se odlučiti da promeni *karijeru* i počne da radi nešto drugo. (Maybe they will decide to change careers and start doing something else.)
5. On je imao dugu i uspešnu *karijeru*. (He had a long and successful career.)